.@edyong209 @ivanoransky  But if you want to claim the whole system is broken please show us data not anecdotes. (fin)
.@edyong209 @ivanoransky Is there a false positive/false negative rate? Yes. Do sometimes people make questionable decisions? Yes. (3/n)

.@edyong209 @ivanoransky Peer review is a demanding and thankless task that I and many of my colleagues take very seriously (1/n)
